titles.title: Providing for the reappointment of Walter E. Massey as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on House Administration.

bill.summary:
2/13/2007--Introduced.
Reappoints Walter E. Massey as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.
